summary: This is a brief email chain forwarding notes from a proffer session related to Epstein witnesses. The email indicates someone else had already taken action and that files would be renamed by the end of the weekend.

events.title: Proffer Session
events.description: A proffer session was conducted, notes from which are being forwarded in this email chain.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain dated December 5, 2019, forwarding notes from a proffer session.
The proffer session occurred on December 4, 2019, and is related to Epstein witnesses.
The email mentions that someone else had already taken action regarding the notes.
The sender states they will have all files renamed by the end of the weekend.
